  <evidence rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">Valve also stores on a users hard drive a unique authorization key or CD-Key that is either entered by the user or downloaded automatically during product registration This authorization key is used to identify a user as valid and allow access to Valve s products services and third party games This key is necessary for Valve to supply any products and services subscribed by users</evidence>
